{"lemma":"رَحْمَةُ","slug":"رَحْمَةُ","root":"ر.ح.م","root_slug":"ر-ح-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ح-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رَحْمَة","root":"رحم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":114},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15076","n15087","n15088"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of رَحِمَ (raḥima) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of رَحِمَ (raḥima)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mercy, compassion, commiseration"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pardon"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew רַחֲמִים (raḥămīm, “mercy”)."},"ipa":["/raħ.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15076","headword_ar":"رَحِمَهُ","root":"rHm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHomapN","text_ar":"رَحْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHomN","text_ar":"رُحْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHamapN","text_ar":"رَحَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHumN","text_ar":"رُحُمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maroHamapN","text_ar":"مَرْحَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * Msb, K, *) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had mercy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compassion, on him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he treated him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regarded him, with mercy"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pity"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compassion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, tender"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender-hearted"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"towards him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclined to favour him"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to benefit him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Msb, K: [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raximahu","text_ar":"رَخِمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxamahu","text_ar":"رَخَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he pardoned him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forgave him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) said of a man: (S, Msb, K:) and also of God [in the former sense, but tropically, or anthropopathically: or as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He favoured him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"benefited him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pardoned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forgave, him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see explanations of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHomapN","text_ar":"رَحْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below]: (Msb, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trH~m","text_ar":"ترحّم","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (MA, [and the same seems to be indicated in the S,]) said of a man: (S:) [and so does ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trH~mhu","text_ar":"ترحّمهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (occurring in the S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rEY","text_ar":"رعى"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.,) accord. to Ibn-Maaroof, for he says that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraH~umN","text_ar":"تَرَحُّمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regarding"},{"kind":"text","text":"[another]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with mercy"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pity"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compassion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pardoning"},{"kind":"text","text":"[him], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forgiving"},{"kind":"text","text":"[him]: and also the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being merciful"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pitiful"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compassionate"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"favourably inclined"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY gayorihi","text_ar":"عَلَى غَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to another"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (KL: but respecting this latter verb, see 2.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHumato","text_ar":"رَحُمَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHimato","text_ar":"رَحِمَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHimato","text_ar":"رُحِمَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaAmapN","text_ar":"رَحَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) which is of the first, (S, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHamN","text_ar":"رَحَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) which is of the second, (S, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHomN","text_ar":"رَحْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is of the third, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She had a complaint of her womb after bringing forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and died in consequence thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) said of a camel, (S, TA,) and of a ewe or goat, and of a woman, and of any animal having a womb: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she had a disease in her womb, in consequence of which she did not receive impregnation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she brought forth without letting fall her secundine:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or, accord. to Lh, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bringing forth without letting fall her secundine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"by a sheep or goat, is termed ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHaAmN","text_ar":"رُحَامٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHima","text_ar":"رَحِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHamN","text_ar":"رَحَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is also said of a water-skin, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was left,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"neglected, by its owners, after its being seasoned with rob,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gyth","text_ar":"غيته"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bEd","text_ar":"بعد"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gyth","text_ar":"غيته"},{"kind":"text","text":", an evident mistranscription, I read, conjecturally,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tamotiynihi","text_ar":"تَمْتِينِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as the only word at all resembling"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gyth","text_ar":"غيته"},{"kind":"text","text":", that I can call to mind, having an apposite signification,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and they did not anoint it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grease it, so that it became spoilt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a bad state, and did not retain the water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the epithet applied to it in this case is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHimN","text_ar":"رَحِمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaAmapN","text_ar":"رَحَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also an inf. n. [of which the verb, if it have one, is app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHuma","text_ar":"رَحُمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being connected by relationship."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n15087","headword_ar":"رَحْمَةٌ","root":"rHm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHamapN","text_ar":"رَحَمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHomN","text_ar":"رُحْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHumN","text_ar":"رُحُمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) thus in a verse of Zuheyr, (S, TA,) and thus in the Kur xviii. 80 accord. to the reading of Aboo-'Amr Ibn-El-'Alà, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maroHamapN","text_ar":"مَرْحَمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) of which last"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraAHimu","text_ar":"مَرَاحِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl., (TA,) [all inf. ns.; when used as simple substs. signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mercy, pity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compassion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenderness"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, and Bd on the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"basomalap","text_ar":"بَسْمَلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of heart;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd ibid.;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclination to favour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclination requiring the exercise of favour and beneficence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd ubi suprà:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pardon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forgiveness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) accord. to Er-Rághib,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHomapN","text_ar":"رَحْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenderness requiring the exercise of beneficence towards the object thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it is used sometimes as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenderness divested of any other attribute:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneficence divested of tenderness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as when it is used as an attribute of the Creator: when used as an attribute of men, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenderness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclination to favour"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without necessarily implying beneficence"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: accord. to El-Káshánee, it is of two kinds; namely, gratuitous, and obligatory: the former is that which pours forth favours, or benefits, antecedently to works; and this is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rHmp","text_ar":"رحمة"},{"kind":"text","text":"that embraces everything: the obligatory is that which is promised to the pious and the doers of good, in the Kur vii. 155 and vii. 54: but this, he says, is included in the gratuitous, because the promise to bestow it for works is purely gratuitous: accord. to the explanation of the Imám Aboo-Is-hák Ahmad Ibn-Mohammad-Ibn-Ibráheem Eth-Thaalebee, it is God's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desire to do good to the deserving thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so that it is an essential attribute: or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abstaining from punishing him who deserves punishment, and doing good to him who does not deserve"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"this"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; so that it is an attribute of operation. (TA.) The saying in the Kur [xxi. 75]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA^adoxalonaAhu","text_ar":"وَاَدْخَلْنَاهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY raHomatinaA","text_ar":"فِى رَحْمَتِنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And we caused him to enter into our mercy"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is tropical: so says IJ. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@ll~`hu","text_ar":"وَا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaxotaS~u biraHomatihi mano ya$aA='u","text_ar":"يَخْتَصُّ بِرَحْمَتِهِ مَنْ يَشَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [ii. 99 and iii. 67], means (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And God distinguishes"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his gift of prophecy"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whom He will"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his prophetic office"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commission."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHomapN","text_ar":"رَحْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sustenance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"means of subsistence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is said to be its meaning as used in the Kur xli. 50. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) so in the Kur vii. 55. (Bd, Jel.) ―         -b5-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Plenty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundance of herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the goods, conveniences,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comforts, of life:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the Kur x. 22 and xxx. 35. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","Sb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n15088","headword_ar":"رَحَمَةٌ","root":"rHm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}